Driver: San Francisco is an action-adventure racing video game developed by Ubisoft Reflections and published by Ubisoft. The game formally was unveiled at E3 2010 and was released in Australia on September 1, 2011, Europe on September 2, 2011 and North America on September 6, 2011 [3] on PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360,[6] while the Microsoft Windows version was released on 27 September 2011.
